data.description: This lovely home has the best of both worlds; quiet forested appeal outdoors with modern updates indoors. Almost 3000 sq ft. Newly rehabbed in 2021 with new vinyl siding, windows, floors, counters, recess lighting, HVAC, updated kitchen, and bathrooms. Large eat-in kitchen with butcher block counter and stainless-steel appliances. Lots of space for entertaining with living room and family room w/ skylight. French doors lead to a patio and huge fully fenced backyard. Sizable office with barn doors. Downstairs bedroom with en-suite and a separate outdoor entrance is an ideal in-law suite or guest room. Spacious owner's suite with a large walk-in closet. Small spare room upstairs currently used as a bedroom would make a perfect play room, nursery, or office. Radiator heat source is not connected. Whole house water filtration system. New gas line capped off. Centrally located in Newport News, just minutes away from Lion's bridge and a beautiful view of the James River.
